QuestData.Title: Gurgl and the Bandit
QuestData.Description:
We've got all the pets back except Gurgl. $n, we need to get that pet back for Breanni.
Stringfellowe saw a nook where we think the leader of these pet poachers is hiding out.
Let's get 'em!
QuestData.LogDescription: Find and battle the leader of the pet poachers.
